<i>noun</i>: 호언장담 [호언장담], 호언 [호언], 객기 [객끼] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호언장담 [호언장담]</dt><br>
<dd>confident remark; bravado</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 목적을 이루겠다고 씩씩하고 자신 있게 하는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>One's remark bravely made with confidence that one will achieve a certain goal.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>호언 [호언]</dt><br>
<dd>confident remark; bravado</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 목적을 이루겠다고 씩씩하게 하는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>One's remark made in a confident manner that one will achieve a certain goal.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>객기 [객끼]</dt><br>
<dd>bravado</dd><br>
<dd>즉흥적 감정으로 인하여 쓸데없이 부리는 용기.</dd><br>
<dd>Impromptu boldness which is not very useful.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>